                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 51.7328em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">按照上述设定后</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">,</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">重新打开浏览器</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">,</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">进入智能模块管理功能</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">,</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">再点击</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">“</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">开始远程维护</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">”</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">，然后在</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_53">“</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_53">打开网 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 53.0328em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_09">络和共享中心</span><span class="stl_51 stl_08 stl_09">&gt;</span><span class="stl_44 stl_08 stl_09">更改适配器设置”可以进行确认极智通虚拟网卡是否连接： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 63.3549em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_24 stl_08 stl_09">4-3</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">、产品类型管理 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 66.3197em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09">4-3-1</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09">、产品类型的新建 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 68.6078em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">在确定生产设备与 </span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">连接、</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">与 </span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">连接并确保 </span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">PLC</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">、</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">启动之后，访问</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">企业管理</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_54" style="word-spacing:-0.0321em;">&gt; &nbsp;</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
