                <div class="stl_05 stl_06">
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 15.1447em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09">4-3-2</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09">、监控数据的新建 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.4328em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_18">建立产品类型之后，现在可以在该产品类型里添加需要监控的数据了。具体监控数据的添加请进 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 18.7328em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">入“企业管理</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_09">&gt;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">监控管理”。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 38.9911em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_34 stl_08 stl_09">监控数据添加具体操作如下： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.5495em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.5495em; left:8.067em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">第一步：在监控数据一览下先选择产品类型，再点击“新建”按钮。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 49.1078em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 49.1078em; left:8.0757em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">第二步：点击</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">新建</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">按钮后，将跳出</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">新建数据监控点</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">的对话框，请输入相关正确信息之后，再 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 50.4078em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_59">点击对话框的</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_59">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_59">新建</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_59">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_59">按钮。之后系统会自动返回到</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_59">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_59">监控数据一览</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_59">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_59">菜单。然后重复新建监控数据的操作， &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 51.7078em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">直至所有的监控数据添加完成。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
