            <div class="stl_view">
                <div class="stl_05 stl_06">
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.7447em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09">4-4-1</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09">、设备指定产品类型 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 20.0328em; left:7.5008em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">在</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">设备管理</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">&gt;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">产品管理</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">里，即使 </span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">跟 </span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">连接成功，如果此时没有指定产品类型，在</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_63" style="word-spacing:-0.0291em;">产品 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.3328em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">类型”菜单下该栏是空的，显示如下： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 28.5911em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_34 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">在 </span><span class="stl_64 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_34 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">添加产品类型具体操作如下： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 30.1495em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 30.1495em; left:8.067em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">第一步：选中未指定产品类型的模块，然后点“编辑”按钮。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 37.6495em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 37.6495em; left:8.0757em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">第二步：点击</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">编辑</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">按钮之后，系统会自动跳出</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">编辑产品信息</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_33">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">的对话框，此时选择已经新建好 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 38.9495em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_61">的产品类型，输入生产时间、安装时间，然后点击</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_61">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_61">保存</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_61">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_61">按钮，就指定成功了。此时</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_61">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_61">产品管理</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_61">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_61">菜单就 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.2495em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">能显示该产品类型的信息了。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 59.2078em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 59.2078em; left:8.0678em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">第三步：再点击菜单左边的</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_65">“+”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">，先点击</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_65">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">下发</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_65">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">，再点击</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_65">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">刷新</span><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_65">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_65">，就能显示该产品类型的监控数据 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 60.5078em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">了。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
